觀光業是'''比利時'''最重要的產業之一，其便利的交通使得其成為歐洲最熱門的旅遊目的地之一。旅遊業貢獻了比利時2.8%的GDP和3.3%的工作崗位（142,000人）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flandersnews.be/cm/flandersnews.be/Flanders%2BToday/tourism/070302_WECOFORUM |title=More support for tourism |publisher=flandersnews.be |date=2007-03-02 |accessdate=2007-03-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070305183324/http://www.flandersnews.be/cm/flandersnews.be/Flanders%2BToday/tourism/070302_WECOFORUM |archivedate=2007-03-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2005年，有670萬國際遊客到訪比利時<ref name="Travel and Tourism in Belgium">[http://www.euromonitor.com/Travel_and_Tourism_in_Belgium Travel and Tourism in Belgium] {{Wayback|url=http://www.euromonitor.com/Travel_and_Tourism_in_Belgium |date=20110105024246 }} - euromonitor.com</ref>，其中三分之二來自鄰近的法國、西班牙和義大利。2007年，比利時在世界旅遊競爭力排名第21位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.weforum.org/en/initiatives/gcp/TravelandTourismReport/CompetitivenessIndex/index.htm |title=Travel and Tourism Competitiveness Index |publisher=World Economic Forum |date=2007-03-01 |accessdate=2007-03-02 |archive-date=2010-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101121101741/http://www.weforum.org/en/initiatives/gcp/TravelandTourismReport/CompetitivenessIndex/index.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年，比利時的主要國際遊客數來源國家如下<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://statbel.fgov.be/fr/binaries/Tourisme%20selon%20pays%20de%20provenance-2014_tcm326-274580.xls |title=Tourisme selon pays de provenance 2014 |accessdate=2016-02-02 |archive-date=2016-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020200306/http://statbel.fgov.be/fr/binaries/Tourisme%20selon%20pays%20de%20provenance-2014_tcm326-274580.xls |dead-url=no }}</ref>：
